OL,6,FThis is less than its previous
OL,7,Fprediction in June when it estimated
OL,8,Fthat the cap would rise by 9.9% to
OL,9,F#1,723.
OL,11,FBut the group said there is also
OL,12,Flikely to be a further "modest"
OL,13,Fincrease in January 2025, with more
OL,14,Frises possible early in the new year
OL,15,Fdue to "recent tensions in the Russia-
OL,16,FUkraine war".
OL,18,FEnergy regulator Ofgem will announce
OL,19,Fthe energy price cap for October to
OL,20,FDecember on August 23.
