OL,6,F"This is not the news households want
OL,7,Fto hear when moving into the colder
OL,8,Fmonths," Craig Lowrey, principal
OL,9,Fconsultant at Cornwall Insight, said.
OL,11,F"Following two consecutive falls in
OL,12,Fthe cap, I'm sure many hoped we were
OL,13,Fon a steady path back to pre-crisis
OL,14,Fprices."
OL,16,FBut he added that the "lingering
OL,17,Fimpact of the energy crisis has left
OL,18,Fus with a market that's still highly
OL,19,Fvolatile".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
