OL,6,F"Despite this, while we don't expect a
OL,7,Freturn to the extreme prices of recent
OL,8,Fyears, it's unlikely that bills will
OL,9,Freturn to what was once considered
OL,10,Fnormal.
OL,12,F"Without significant intervention,
OL,13,Fthis may well be the new normal."
OL,15,FOfgem changes the price cap every
OL,16,Fthree months based on several factors,
OL,17,Fthe most important of which is the
OL,18,Fprice of energy in wholesale markets.
