OL,11,FOfgem is currently considering the
OL,12,Ffuture of price protection, including
OL,13,Fthe suitability of the price cap and a
OL,14,Fpotential permanent ban on so-called
OL,15,Facquisition tariffs - cheaper prices
OL,16,Ffor new customers to lure them away
OL,17,Ffrom their existing suppliers.
