OL,3,CEnergy bills expected to rise by #146
OL,4,Cahead of winter months
OL,6,FCornwall Insight is calling for a
OL,7,Freform of the price cap or
OL,8,Fintroduction of social tariffs, but
OL,9,Fwarned longer-term solutions were also
OL,10,Fvital.
OL,12,FMr Lowrey said: "Immediate action is
OL,13,Fneeded to ease the financial burden on
OL,14,Fhouseholds - such as the introduction
OL,15,Fof social tariffs, or reform of the
OL,16,Fprice cap ` but that's only part of
OL,17,Fthe solution.
