OL,6,F"We must also develop a long-term
OL,7,Fstrategy to secure our energy future.
OL,8,FThis means a fundamental overhaul of
OL,9,Four energy system, with a strong
OL,10,Femphasis on increasing domestic energy
OL,11,Fproduction.
OL,13,F"Simply waiting for prices to drop on
OL,14,Ftheir own isn't an option, we need a
OL,15,Fproactive and forward-thinking
OL,16,Fapproach to ensure long lasting energy
OL,17,Faffordability and security."
